# FILE: halabFreelance/serviceCatalog/serviceCatalog.desc
# ROLE: Category Deep-Dive & Service Exploration
# ROUTE: /freelance/catalog/:category
# ACCOUNT: All types can browse — hiring open to all registered users
# THEME: Dark · grid-heavy · filter-focus

## 1. CATEGORY HEADER (Top Fold)
- BG: blurred dark image matching category + indigo/purple gradient overlay
- BREADCRUMB: الرئيسية > المستقلون > [Category]
- TITLE: emoji + Arabic category name (gradient-text on keyword)
- SUBTITLE: "اكتشف خدمات متخصصة من أفضل المواهب الأكاديمية"

## 2. FILTER SIDEBAR / TOP BAR
- SEARCH: within-category search input
- FREELANCER TYPE: [🎓 طلابي] [💼 خارجي] [الكل]
  - Shows student freelancers (isFreelancer: true) vs external (businessType: 'freelancer')
- SERVICE LEVEL: [🥉 مبتدئ] [🥈 محترف] [🥇 نخبة]
- PRICE RANGE: SYP slider
- DELIVERY TIME: [⚡ سريع 24س] [🕒 قياسي] [🗓️ مخصص]
- SORT: الأعلى تقييماً · الأقل سعراً · الأحدث

## 3. SERVICE GRID
- GRID: grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 · gap-6
- SERVICE CARD:
  - COVER IMAGE: service thumbnail · aspect-video · rounded-xl
  - FREELANCER ROW: avatar + name + verified badge + TYPE badge
    - "مستقل طلابي" — indigo pill
    - "مستقل خارجي" — amber pill
  - TITLE: text-[#F1F5F9] font-medium
  - PRICE: "يبدأ من 150,000 SYP"
  - STATS: ⭐ rating (count) · 📦 orders in queue
- PROMOTED SLOTS: first 2 cards get border-[#6366F1]/40 + subtle glow

## 4. SERVICE LIGHTBOX (Quick View Modal)
- Clicking a card → modal with full details before navigating to service page
- INCLUDES: revisions count · delivery days · source code included?
- ACTIONS: [💳 اطلب الآن] [💬 استفسار]

## 5. FOOTER (Can't Find It?)
- CTA: [📝 انشر طلبك الخاص] → custom task posting form
  - Freelancers can bid on client's specific requirements
